{"id":1654742,"retrievedAt":"2026-03-20T11:51:36.128Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/llyH4rIzzepae4tkyu0kmnaMl17.jpg","belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[],"homepage":"https://milanmachinimafestival.org/pastinaca-videotapes-plantation-2026","id":1654742,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["HK","KZ","CH"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Cold Cakes / 冰冷的蛋糕 / コールド・ケーキ","overview":"Built within the 3D worlds of Grand Theft Auto: San Andreas, Condemned 2: Bloodshot, Call of Duty: Black Ops II, Saw II: Flesh & Blood, and Call of Duty: Advanced Warfare, Pastinaca Videotapes Plantation’s machinima exploit each engine’s abrupt, uncanny atmosphere, creating bizarre collages that challenge any single interpretative move. Cold Cakes / 冰冷的蛋糕 / コールド・ケーキ is no exception and adopts the look of damaged evidence. Burnt-in timestamps, murky contrast, smeared textures, and VHS-like degradation give the film the texture of a copied, handled, and partially lost recording. Moving between domestic interiors, found footage, flickering images, bodily aftermath, cryptic imagery and open-world urban drift, the film assembles fragments rather than a linear narrative. Working through a text-first method that pairs written themes with archival and game footage, PVP reflects on suppressed histories, hoaxes, mockumentaries, and the erasure of inconvenient events.","popularity":0.0071,"poster_path":"/v3fWKfA3YqmF3aPhwCj6pWtNvMW.jpg","production_companies":[],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"HK","name":"Hong Kong"},{"iso_3166_1":"KZ","name":"Kazakhstan"},{"iso_3166_1":"CH","name":"Switzerland"}],"release_date":"2026-03-18","revenue":0,"runtime":12,"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English"}],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Cold Cakes / 冰冷的蛋糕 / コールド・ケーキ","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[],"crew":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":5043954,"known_for_de